  "title": "-NEW- Perm Facilities Coordination Administrator",
  "description": "<p>Job Responsibilities:</p><p>·      \nManage\ninternal and external mail and courier services, including document and parcel\nhandling.</p><p>·      \nSupport\ndocument distribution and records management to ensure accuracy and service\nquality.</p><p>·      \nSet up,\nreset, and maintain conference rooms and meeting facilities.</p><p>·      \nCoordinate\nrepair and maintenance of office equipment and facilities.</p><p>·      \nManage\ninternal staff relocation and office moves.</p><p>·      \nAssist\nwith furniture installation, fixing, and maintenance.</p><p>·      \nSupport\nprocurement activities, including sourcing and ad-hoc outdoor purchasing when\nrequired.</p><p>·      \nAssist\nwith daily office operations, including security systems, maintenance, cleaning\nservices, and handling staff enquiries, requests, and complaints.</p><p>·      \nPerform\nad-hoc administrative and operational duties as assigned.</p><p>·      \nAdhoc tasks and projects as assigned<br />\n<br />\n</p><p>Job Requirements</p><p>·      \nMinimum Diploma in a related discipline</p><p>·      \nMinimum 3 year of relevant facilities/office\nadministrative experience  </p><p>·      \nAble to start immediately or within short\nnotice</p><p><br />\n<br />\n</p><p>Interested candidates, kindly email your detailed resumes\nin MS word format to <a href=\"mailto:josephkoh@recruitexpress.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">joseph.koh@ambition.com.sg</a> </p><p>Attention to Joseph Koh Wei Jie (R1873431)</p><p>Shortlisted candidates will be notified</p><p><a href=\"http://www.ambition.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">www.ambition.com.sg</a></p><p>EA Registration Number: R1873431</p><p>Data provided is for recruitment purposes only</p><p>Business Registration Number: 200611680D. License Number:\n10C5117</p>",
